## Memory ‚Äî Start of Every Session

Before doing any work, check for relevant context from previous sessions:

1. Use the `mem-search` tool to search for related bugs, decisions, or patterns
2. Check `MEMORY.md` in the project root for the index of accumulated knowledge
3. If the task touches a previous bug or architectural decision, use `get_observations` to fetch full details before proposing changes

This prevents re-introducing fixed bugs and re-litigating settled architectural decisions.

