## Commands

### Backend
```bash
# Start dev server (from project root)
uvicorn backend.main:app --reload --port 8000

# Install dependencies
pip install -r backend/requirements.txt
```

### Frontend
```bash
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev        # starts Vite on http://localhost:5173
npm run build      # production build (use to verify no compile errors)
```

### Tests
```bash
# Run the full core API flow test suite (requires backend running on :8000)
python tests/test_core_flow.py

# Run with a real provider key to test live proxy
TEST_OPENAI_KEY=sk-... python tests/test_core_flow.py
```

