# AIRent ‚Äî Project System Design Reference

> **Read this before touching any code.** Single source of truth for architecture,
> data model, business logic, and conventions.

---

## 1. What Is AIRent?

AIRent is a **SaaS marketplace** where users rent time-limited virtual API keys to
access top AI models (OpenAI, Anthropic, Google Gemini) without needing their own
provider accounts. Owner: **Deepanshu Sharma** (sole developer).

**Core concept:** User pays once ‚Üí gets a virtual key ‚Üí key works for N
minutes/hours/day and up to T tokens ‚Üí key auto-expires ‚Üí user can buy again.

