## 3. Environment Variables

| Variable | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `DATABASE_URL` | SQLite / Postgres connection string |
| `REDIS_URL` | Redis (cache + rate limiting) |
| `SECRET_KEY` | JWT signing |
| `CASHFREE_CLIENT_ID/SECRET` | Payment gateway credentials |
| `CASHFREE_ENVIRONMENT` | `sandbox` or `production` |
| `CASHFREE_WEBHOOK_SECRET` | Webhook HMAC-SHA256 verification |
| `SMTP_HOST/PORT/USER/PASSWORD` | Transactional email |
| `ADMIN_NOTIFICATION_EMAIL` | Where spending alerts go |
| `VITE_API_URL` | Frontend ‚Üí backend base URL |
| `VITE_CASHFREE_ENV` | `sandbox` or `production` |

