|---|---|
| `POST /auth/register` | Create account |
| `POST /auth/login` | Get JWT |
| `GET /api/plans` | List active plans (includes model_id, duration_label) |
| `GET /api/active-providers` | Which provider enums have ‚â•1 active key |
| `GET /status/` | Provider health |
| `POST /api/webhooks/cashfree` | Payment webhook (HMAC verified) |

### Authenticated user
| Path | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `POST /api/checkout/session` | Create Cashfree order ‚Üí `payment_session_id` |
| `GET /api/checkout/verify/{order_id}` | Verify payment |
| `GET /api/rentals/active` | Live rentals |
| `GET /api/rentals/history` | Past rentals |
| `GET /api/invoice/{rental_id}/html` | HTML receipt |
| `WS /ws/usage/{rental_id}` | Real-time token/expiry events |
| `POST /v1/chat/completions` | OpenAI-compatible proxy |

### Admin (`/admin/*`)
Plans, Users, ProviderKeys, Stats, Analytics, Alerts, CSV export ‚Äî all behind `role=ADMIN`.

