## 6. Marketplace Buying Flow

```
/marketplace
    ‚îÇ
    ‚îú‚îÄ 1. GET /api/active-providers  ‚Üí filter MODEL_CATALOGUE
    ‚îú‚îÄ 2. GET /api/plans             ‚Üí flat list with model_id + duration_minutes
    ‚îÇ
    ‚ñº
Step 1 ‚Äî Pick model   (only shows models whose providerKey is active)
Step 2 ‚Äî Pick duration (button disabled if no plan exists for that combo)
Step 3 ‚Äî Review card  (token cap, RPM, price)  ‚Üí  "Rent Now"
    ‚îÇ
    ‚îú‚îÄ POST /api/checkout/session ‚Üí { payment_session_id }
    ‚îú‚îÄ Cashfree JS SDK opens payment sheet
    ‚îú‚îÄ On success ‚Üí redirect /dashboard?payment=success&order_id=xxx
    ‚îî‚îÄ Webhook creates Rental + emails virtual key
```

**matchPlan logic (Marketplace.jsx):**
1. Exact match: `plan.model_id === selectedModel && plan.duration_minutes === dur.minutes`
2. Fallback: universal plan (`plan.model_id === null`) with matching duration

---

## 7. Token Cap Formula

```
BASE_TOKENS = { 15min: 20K, 1hr: 80K, 6hr: 400K, 24hr: 1.2M }

drain_rate per model:
  gemini-1.5-flash          ‚Üí  1√ó
  gpt-4o-mini               ‚Üí  3√ó
  gemini-1.5-pro            ‚Üí  5√ó
  claude-3-5-sonnet-20241022 ‚Üí 8√ó
  gpt-4o                    ‚Üí 10√ó

token_cap = BASE_TOKENS[duration] / drain_rate
```
AdminPanel PlansTab auto-fills this when you pick a model + duration.

---

## 8. Payment Flow (Cashfree)

```
order_id convention:  order_{plan_id}_{user_id}_{unix_timestamp}

1. POST /api/checkout/session
   ‚Üí create Cashfree order via REST API
   ‚Üí return { payment_session_id }

2. Frontend: window.Cashfree({ mode }).checkout({ paymentSessionId })
   ‚Üí Cashfree redirects to /dashboard?payment=success&order_id=xxx

3. POST /api/webhooks/cashfree  (PAYMENT_SUCCESS_WEBHOOK)
   ‚Üí verify HMAC-SHA256(timestamp + raw_body, CASHFREE_WEBHOOK_SECRET)
   ‚Üí _parse_order_id(order_id) ‚Üí plan_id, user_id
   ‚Üí create Rental, send email with virtual key
```

---

## 9. Proxy Flow

```
POST /v1/chat/completions  (Authorization: Bearer vk_xxx)
  ‚Üí validate virtual key (Redis ‚Üí DB)
  ‚Üí check rental: ACTIVE + tokens_remaining > 0 + not expired
  ‚Üí IP-pin check
  ‚Üí regex PII filter (email, phone, SSN, card numbers)
  ‚Üí Gemini Flash AI safety pre-scan
  ‚Üí Redis semantic cache lookup
  ‚Üí forward to provider via LiteLLM
  ‚Üí deduct tokens, log to UsageLog
  ‚Üí return / stream response
```

