## 10. Frontend Design System

### Colours
| Role | Value |
|---|---|
| Background | `#07070f` |
| Primary gradient | `from-violet-600 to-fuchsia-600` |
| Success | `emerald-400` |
| Warning | `amber-400` |
| Danger | `rose-400` |
| Subtle border | `border-white/[0.08]` |
| Hover border | `border-white/[0.16]` |

### CSS utilities (index.css)
- `.glass-card` ‚Äî `bg-white/[0.03] backdrop-blur-xl`
- `.gradient-text` ‚Äî violet‚Üífuchsia gradient text
- `.grid-pattern` ‚Äî subtle background grid overlay
- `.blob-1/2/3` ‚Äî animated ambient colour blobs
- `.shimmer-text` ‚Äî animated shimmer effect

### Motion (src/lib/motion.js)
```js
fadeUp, fadeIn, fadeLeft, fadeRight   // entrance animations
staggerContainer(delay)               // stagger children
scaleIn                               // scale + fade entrance
viewport = { once: true, amount: 0.2 }
```

### Component conventions
- All authenticated pages: `<Navbar />` + `<Footer />`
- Auth pages: standalone with blob bg + grid-pattern overlay
- Policy pages: `<PolicyPage>`, `<PolicyHero>`, `<PolicySection>` (PolicyLayout.jsx)
- Buttons: `whileHover={{ scale: 1.04 }} whileTap={{ scale: 0.97 }}`
- Step indicators: numbered violet circles with title + subtitle

