## 12. Checklists

### Adding a new AI model
- [ ] `backend/database/models.py` ‚Äî add to `ProviderType` if new provider
- [ ] `frontend/src/pages/Marketplace.jsx` ‚Äî add to `MODEL_CATALOGUE`
- [ ] `frontend/src/pages/Playground.jsx` ‚Äî add to `ALL_MODELS`
- [ ] `frontend/src/pages/AdminPanel.jsx` ‚Äî add to `MODEL_OPTIONS` in PlansTab
- [ ] Admin: add ProviderKey for the provider
- [ ] Admin: create plans (model √ó each duration)

### Adding a new duration option
- [ ] `frontend/src/pages/Marketplace.jsx` ‚Äî add to `DURATIONS`
- [ ] `frontend/src/pages/AdminPanel.jsx` ‚Äî add to `DURATION_PRESETS` with `suggestPrice` and entry in `BASE_TOKENS`
- [ ] Admin: create plans for each model √ó this duration

### Adding a new page
- [ ] Create `frontend/src/pages/NewPage.jsx`
- [ ] Add route in `frontend/src/App.jsx`
- [ ] Add link in `Navbar.jsx` if top-level

